### Restock a product (replace {productId} with actual ID)
# @name restockProduct
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/{productId}/restock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 50
}

### Sell a product (replace {productId} with actual ID)
# @name sellProduct
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/{productId}/sell
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}
